Detailed ASCII Layout Mockup - Single-Column Primary Reading Flow without Photo

Use this wireframe as the structural blueprint for a no-photo variant of the single-column CV. It mirrors the existing single-column template, but the header is reduced to a disciplined left-aligned text stack with no image or substitute decoration.

## Page Format

```text
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ PAGE FORMAT                                                                                  │
│ A4 PORTRAIT                                                                                  │
│ Top margin: 16 mm   Bottom margin: 16 mm   Left margin: 18 mm   Right margin: 18 mm        │
│ Layout: SINGLE COLUMN PRIMARY READING FLOW                                                   │
│ Grid behavior: left-aligned text system with disciplined spacing rhythm                      │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Header Band

```text
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ HEADER BAND                                                                                  │
│                                                                                              │
│  FULL NAME                                                                                   │
│  Professional Title / Positioning Line                                                       │
│  City, Country · Phone · Email · LinkedIn · Website                                          │
│                                                                                              │
│  Optional thin accent rule spanning full usable width below header                           │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

Header rules:

* Use the full content width for text.
* Keep all header lines aligned to the same left edge.
* Do not center the header just because the photo is absent.
* Do not replace the photo with an icon, badge, quote, color block, or decorative shape.
* Preserve clean whitespace to the right as part of the normal page field.

Contact line variants:

```text
City, Country  ·  +00 000 000 000  ·  name@email.com  ·  linkedin.com/in/name  ·  website.com
```

```text
City, Country  ·  +00 000 000 000  ·  name@email.com
linkedin.com/in/name  ·  website.com
```

Suggested header rhythm:

* 8-12 pt from top margin to name
* 4-6 pt from name to title
* 4-6 pt from title to contact line
* 10-14 pt from contact line to divider rule
* 14-18 pt from divider rule to the first section

